body:
`Hash#force_compact` returns a hash with non blank values.

example:

```ruby
hash = { a: true, b: false, c: nil, d: [], e: {}, f: ''}
hash.force_compact # => { a: true}
hash # => { a: true, b: false, c: nil, d: [], e: {}, f: ''}
{ b: false, c: nil, d: [], e: {}, f: '' }.force_compact # => {}
```
